caption: The image is a cartoon drawing of a woman wearing a purple mask and holding a tissue. The text in the image reads "Help stop the spread of Covid-19," "Wear your mask," and "work together." The website www.reallygreatsite.com is also displayed in the image. The image is promoting the importance of wearing masks and working together to stop the spread of the virus.
